    between the left and right margins is determined
    by the value selected.
    If :hp1.left:ehp1. is the attribute value, the text is
    output at the left margin.
    If :hp1.right:ehp1. is the attribute value, the text is
    output next to the right margin.
    When :hp1.center:ehp1. or :hp1.centre:ehp1. is specified,
    the text is centered between the left and right margins.
